<P>
   ITALY-CHAMINADE _ ROME _ About 124-strong, they have arrived,
these loyal Daytonian Catholics. They are here in support of
today's beatification of Father Chaminade, a well-known Catholic
figure in Ohio's Miami Valley area. We get their reaction to being
here, and the strength of emotion that they feel for this man that
would make them travel across the Atlantic to stand for him.
Developing. (Roughton, Cox News Service). WITH PHOTO.
