<P>
   BUSH _ As we pass the traditional Labor Day kickoff for the fall
campaign, we look at George Bush's strategy for victory. Where will
he be campaigning and on what issues? Which groups of voters will
he be trying to sway? What pitfalls must he avoid to win? What are
his chances? (Herman, Austin American-Statesman) MOVED FRIDAY.
